{"tid":1657343,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"劉細良提左我地 下一波應該重點關照嘅商戶","createTime":"2019-10-16T04:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T05:30:03.000Z","uid":184726,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bf4dab4a8424bee565800c4da1cbf74830c23728","tid":1657343,"uid":184726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:53:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係企圖係參議院制止法案嘅相關企業</span></span><br />\n<br />\n基本上中共會動用一切力量阻止人權法案<br />\n估計會有好多商業人士為左利益去參議院進行遊說阻止<br />\n呢班人嘅仆街程度仲衰過伍淑清<br />\n甚至直接上升到黑裝修我覺得都唔過份<br />\n我地唔可以忘記呢班賣港賊<br />\n同埋一定要搵到佢地係香港有咩生意<br />\n我地要比佢地知道 出賣港人係唔會好下場"},{"pid":"22c7c25fc5d528004b82fa153906e3beeb314f1e","tid":1657343,"uid":198590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:53:37.000Z","msg":"1020 到時見!<br />\n<br />\n等我為大家回憶下決定1020去定唔去[2]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1657270\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1657270</a>"},{"pid":"ed4bf71231365854a0a0360b03ab65d7c99c6018","tid":1657343,"uid":184726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:53:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e13c80a03c208db07806e9cdee74c9e9a9cd87fd","tid":1657343,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:53:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dC4rszp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdC4rszp.jpg&h=a54a4986&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e3ff097901bb5b226a9d22b9105a5a48b76f9c46","tid":1657343,"uid":184726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:54:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9913879e247bf23062f4e47e29df73a4d049a40a","tid":1657343,"uid":184726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:55:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f64026cc503880c99715fd4dad0d632c3364da2d","tid":1657343,"uid":184726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:56:30.000Z","msg":"推"},